HOMEWORK 5: LIGHTING

Notes:
    Added lighting to my sword. Diffuse and ambient light contributions can be tweaked in the parameters as described below.

    Tweak the parameters to change the properties of the sword. Normals are generated dynamically with blade geometry!

    Program derived from example 13, provided by professor

Running the program:
    makefile produces an executable named "hw5"
    run with ./hw5

Program controls:
    l ------------------- toggle lighting
    m ------------------- toggle light movement
    [] ------------------ manually move light (if stopped)
    WASD ---------------- rotate scene/view
    Arrow Up/Down ------- select parameters
    Arrow Left/Right ---- modify parameters

Project time:
    Approx 4hrs


ATTRIBUTION:



make clean && make -j &&__NV_PRIME_RENDER_OFFLOAD=1 __VK_LAYER_NV_optimus=NVIDIA_only __GLX_VENDOR_LIBRARY_NAME=nvidia ./project